C
C Common block containing one variable which should be set before a call
C to NODECOORDS. When the variable are set, the flag ERRCOORDS should be set
C to TRUE so that we don't try to output the message with misleading or just
C plain wrong values of ERRNODX and ERRNODY
C
	LOGICAL		 ERRCOORDS
	INTEGER 	 ERRNODX
	INTEGER 	 ERRNODY
C
	COMMON/ERROR/	 ERRCOORDS,ERRNODX,ERRNODY
